Description: Prolog is a logic programming language associated with artificial intelligence and computational linguistics

Program 3: Find out the sum of numbers from 1 to N using ‘cut’ predicate.

Code:
% Base case: Sum of 0 numbers is 0.
sum(0, 0) :- !.
% Recursive case: Sum of N numbers is N plus the sum of the first N-1 numbers.
sum(N, S) :- N1 is N-1, sum(N1, S1), S is S1+N, !.

Queries:
sum(0, X).
sum(10, X).
sum(5, X).

The output of Queries:
X=0
X=55
X=15
